Documentation
-------------

Place the load module tag {cms_module module="touchInlineEdit"} into the head of your template. 
Configure the group permissions for admin users (set permission: Use touchInlineEdit) or optionally 
setup the frontend user support and take a look at the cmsms frontend.

[1]: http://dev.cmsmadesimple.org/projects/touchinlineedit
[2]: http://www.homepage-community.de/index.php?topic=1680.0
